title: We Can Move You by Summer Alan
description: Overview: Josie has been burned, humiliated and forced to quit her job. She's ready to run away--only thing left to do is call the movers and get the hell out. That's the plan. Until they show up. The plan needs to change. Alec and Ethan are the two sexiest men she's ever seen, and aside from being sweet and gorgeous, they want her--right here, right now. Why move? Why not be moved instead, in every possible way imaginable?
